race.comment: GREYSYND QUINN (1) finds it hard to win. Finished second (19.83) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Must come into calculations. TIPSY ETHICS (3) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last five runs. Last time finished 3rd over 388m at Gosford beaten 0.8 lengths (22.30) behind Tip Top Tiger in a Grade 5 on November 4. Overdue and expected to feature again. JAKEY BLUE (6) was a last start winner (19.57) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Has a good record at this journey. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Expecting another bold showing. LEKTRA BERT (2) among the chances again based on last run here.
